              Determine IT system needs for plan payment
            </button>
          </h3>
          <div
            class="usa-accordion__content usa-prose"
            data-testid="accordionItem_determine-it-system-needs-for-plan-payment"
            hidden=""
            id="determine-it-system-needs-for-plan-payment"
          >
            <div
              class="text-light margin-bottom-3 line-height-normal font-body-md"
            >
              <div>
                <p
                  class="margin-top-0 margin-bottom-1"
                >
                  For those models that are adjusting the MAPD payments for their models, the two main systems for Plan Payment are MARx and APPS.
                </p>
                <ul
                  class="padding-left-3 margin-top-0 margin-bottom-1"
                >
                  <li
                    class="line-height-normal"
                  >
                    MARx to enroll and pay plans
                  </li>
                  <li
                    class="line-height-normal"
                  >
                    APPS (automated plan payment system) processes MARx payments to MAPD plans
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p
                  class="margin-top-0 margin-bottom-1"
                >
                  MARx is under the MEPS suite of systems. For APPS, the CM system owner is the Medicare Plan Payment Group (MPPG), Division of Payment Operations (DPO).
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3
            class="usa-accordion__heading"
          >
            <button
              aria-controls="operations-for-each-performance-year-of-the-model"
              aria-expanded="false"
              class="usa-accordion__button"
              data-testid="accordionButton_operations-for-each-performance-year-of-the-model"
              type="button"
            >
              Operations for each performance year of the model
            </button>
          </h3>
          <div
            class="usa-accordion__content usa-prose"
            data-testid="accordionItem_operations-for-each-performance-year-of-the-model"
            hidden=""
            id="operations-for-each-performance-year-of-the-model"
          >
            <div
              class="text-light margin-bottom-3 line-height-normal font-body-md"
            >
              <div>
                <p
                  class="margin-top-0 margin-bottom-1"
                >
                  Several of the processes that were done before the model goes live and described above are repeated annually. Those processes include:
                </p>
                <ul
                  class="padding-left-3 margin-top-0 margin-bottom-1"
                >
                  <li
                    class="line-height-normal"
                  >
                    Update external communications (call letter)
                  </li>
                  <li
                    class="line-height-normal"
                  >
                    Provide new or updated requirements to various HPMS module teams
                  </li>
                  <li
                    class="line-height-normal"
                  >
                    The applications and application review, bid review, formulary review
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
